  "text": "Under both scenarios, population structure is required for the evolution of suicide. This pre-requisite had been previously proposed on the basis of experimental studies with a genetically engineered, suicidal strain of E. coli grown on agar plates [CITATION_1] and is theoretically extended here to a broader spectrum of population structures, suicide efficacies and co-occurring immune mechanisms.",
